snippet.title: Dave.EXE: Vampiric Vacation | Update #4 OUT NOW!!!
snippet.description:
Dave.EXE's Vampiric Vacation update is out now! Two brand new enemies, a new location based off of Dracula's Castle, and more! Not to mention the plethora of QoL changes and fixes featured in this update. Come and give Dave.EXE's newest early access build a shot, only on Patreon.


Special thanks to Padre Snowmizzle for making the trailer ► https://twitter.com/PadreSnowmizzle
